<TEXT>
<P>
Unbeaten Julio Cesar Chavez will move up in weight to challenge World Boxing 
Council super lightweight champion Roger Mayweather on May 13 at the Forum. 
</P>
<P>
The fight, promoted by Don King, will be a rematch of the 1985 meeting when 
Chavez knocked out Mayweather in the second round. 
</P>
