VIOLATIONS; FIRES -- VENTURA COUNTY; HAZARDOUS MATERIALS -- DISPOSAL; 
CHEMICALS; PACIFIC INTERMEDIATES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041289-0056 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 42944 </DOCID>
